Near the Crown Plaza Hotel is The Waterman, which provides English food and a kid-friendly setting.
The Wrestlers is a restaurant located nearby that provides a low priced fast food option, suitable for families as well.
There's a English restaurant with a high customer rating with a price range of 30 euros near All Bar One. It's called Midsummer House.
Alimentum is a 3 star restaurant in city centre next to Yippee Noodle Bar.
Strada is family friendly, has a cheap price range and a customer rating of average.